Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.92,0:00:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.63,0:00:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's big!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.28,0:00:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.01,0:00:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's surprise Tsugumi with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.59,0:03:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I pulled an all-nighter and it's finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.29,0:03:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.58,0:03:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I name it... the Tree Spirit Statue!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.17,0:03:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh crap, I'm running out of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.06,0:04:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.16,0:04:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't bring it along on foot, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.29,0:04:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did Daitetsu say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm beginning to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.23,0:04:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To craft out what you saw in a tree is like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.55,0:04:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this... What a refined human figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I materialized.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.25,0:05:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A vessel that's able to accept me...{tlc:わらわの受容体たり得る依り代など}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.07,0:05:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you must be shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor boy. Just remain like that until you've calmed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.55,0:05:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be afraid, don't be afraid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.31,0:06:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.49,0:06:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's cheap stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.50,0:06:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a million{bajillion} questions to ask you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.55,0:06:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my line.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well, you can ask first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm magnanimous. Speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{Umm}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.06,0:06:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a strong sense for spiritual stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is the first time I can see one so clearly...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.55,0:06:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a ghost... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.03,0:06:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a tree spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.31,0:06:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot believe it's come down to this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.39,0:06:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're likening me to mountain demons? Explain yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:06:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe my child's notion of god has been reduced to such a state. {tlc: わが産子の神観念}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.26,0:07:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time to educate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the first place, what did you take a guardian tree for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sacred tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.02,0:07:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sacred tree is as its name goes, a tree of a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.01,0:07:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A vessel for the god.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.56,0:07:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A land deity had descended upon that big nagi tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.01,0:07:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A land deity is the guardian deity of this land.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.14,0:07:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All living things were born from that land deity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.82,0:07:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That land deity is none other than me. A god that you can call a mother of this land.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does a god just pop out of nowhere like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.30,0:07:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's my turn to ask questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.30,0:07:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this vessel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.11,0:07:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vessel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.29,0:07:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I materialized from.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.76,0:07:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, there was a human shape like this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.18,0:07:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that was a woodcraft that I made.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels very comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:07:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.31,0:08:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, isn't it because it's made out of the sacred tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.85,0:08:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're telling the truth, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.26,0:08:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get struck by lightning if you lie! {You'll be punished (literal)}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.47,0:08:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why do you not know anything about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.73,0:08:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was cut down some time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.26,0:08:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This shrine is undergoing land readjustment. {tlc: 区画整備land readjustment - in simple terms this shrine's land is going to be somebody else's land or is going to be used for some other purpose}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.22,0:08:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the deity is to be enshrined together in a nearby shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.08,0:08:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A friend gave me that sacred tree,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.66,0:08:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I made a woodcraft out of it for a district exhibition. {tlc: 地区展}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place was my childhood playground. I was shocked too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, haven't we met there before? In the past-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You deserve to be struck by lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How... How horrendous! {tlc:なんたる・・・なんたるちーや・・・！} {<- aren't they trying to mimic french or itallian or whatever opera?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.09,0:08:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you cut down a sacred tree and made it into a woodcraft!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dismemberment murder case!{haha higurashi}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.21,0:08:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How... how horrendous!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:09:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now is not the time to be singing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.07,0:09:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe things turn out like this while I was asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.94,0:09:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How horrendous local administration work is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.69,0:09:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still remember? In the past, you and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.86,0:09:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no memories of such things!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.86,0:09:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think will happen if the guardian tree has fallen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.68,0:09:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The land for appeasing the god will lose its guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.72,0:09:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will become of my lovely children, my followers?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.45,0:09:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This land will become insecure, and calamities will spread.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.76,0:09:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody has to bring peace to this land...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.03,0:09:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How miserable!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.73,0:09:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to do with this puny split-spirit of a god...{tlc:分身霊}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erm... a bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.87,0:09:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw it, you non-believer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.99,0:09:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an impurity!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.29,0:09:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The things that were suppressed by the sacred tree are all coming alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.86,0:10:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No point making that expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.55,0:10:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think you're able to touch this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A human can't hold it in the first place, and{even if you do} you'll just get tainted, though not as much as me. {tlc}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ewww, dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the name of god?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.29,0:10:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.79,0:10:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want something to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.84,0:10:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any offerings though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.56,0:10:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go buy some.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a god...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.62,0:10:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no countermeasures against the impurities infesting this land...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.29,0:10:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I even lost my dignity for being saved by a non-believer...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you call yourself a god...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.62,0:11:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I kill that bug?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With a flick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.81,0:11:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That only returned to the land. It'll reappear as a new impurity, given time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.41,0:11:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the exception of those who have undergone training,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.88,0:11:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,normal people can't touch the impurities.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who exactly are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.45,0:11:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a strong sense for the supernatural, maybe that's why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.15,0:11:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many things that I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.15,0:11:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me think for a while. Don't talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.58,0:11:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like silence; can I turn on the TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.57,0:11:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! TV, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.83,0:11:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.37,0:11:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.21,0:11:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.07,0:11:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.84,0:11:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.19,0:11:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just pass it to me! {TLC}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.43,0:11:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, which one should I press?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Press~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.70,0:11:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magical Girl Lolikko Cutie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.23,0:12:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.22,0:12:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that's the TV I've heard about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.01,0:12:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pictures are moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.75,0:12:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of trick is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.65,0:12:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may just continue to watch. {tlc}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.26,0:12:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the name of love and justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat this! Magical Funny Stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.23,0:12:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an eye-opener. I'm starting to feel that this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.70,0:12:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have writing papers?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.91,0:12:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Writing? You mean calligraphy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.29,0:12:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time for revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spare me that, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sword or fire has no effect on impurities.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.81,0:12:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That being said, I'll get tainted if I touch them with my bare hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.20,0:12:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Woah, an outbreak of spiders. Creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.04,0:12:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spiders are creepy? Nice pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.95,0:12:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exorcism is needed to cleanse the impurities.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.47,0:12:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means the purifying power of a god is effective against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:13:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't summon that much power with this body.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.67,0:13:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I just have to compensate with an external option.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In short, an exorcist item!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.07,0:13:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A beautiful young girl, a land deity and a guardian deity!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.13,0:13:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive the impurities!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.68,0:13:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The streamers on my exorcist item, gather the purifying power of the gods!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.70,0:13:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A powerful weapon that crushes the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.46,0:13:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erm, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and catch them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.71,0:13:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.06,0:13:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.52,0:13:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.93,0:13:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This! This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.89,0:13:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just need to eliminate the impurities in the name of love and justice, just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.25,0:13:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't tell you my name yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.41,0:13:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same name as the tree. Easy to remember, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.68,0:13:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.52,0:14:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin. Mikuriya Jin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.60,0:14:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.90,0:14:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry. Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.45,0:14:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home... where?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.85,0:14:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked for a tai fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.44,0:14:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's also a tai. A real tai is too expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.80,0:14:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get struck by lightning if you scrimp on the offerings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.67,0:14:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Considering that in the past they would have offered fresh tai in various occasions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.90,0:14:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fresh offerings?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.65,0:14:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice pun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.00,0:14:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.49,0:14:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll make do with this for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.14,0:14:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want a real tai for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.51,0:15:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is also delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.09,0:15:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really have nowhere to return to?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.71,0:15:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sacred tree has become like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.58,0:15:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should understand. {tlc}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.07,0:15:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that doesn't fit your image... {tlc}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.74,0:15:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it your fault to begin with that you made such a vessel?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.68,0:15:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.56,0:15:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to weasel out now? {tlc}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.64,0:15:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wipe away the bean paste please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.38,0:15:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhow, I need your power to cleanse the impurities, just like earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.14,0:15:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously it's better to stay with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.21,0:15:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.99,0:15:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calamities will spread if the number of impurities increase.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In short, it's all for the sake of this land.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.70,0:15:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just accept that fact and let me stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.58,0:15:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for the news{It's news channel time}. {need edit, too literal}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.48,0:15:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Firstly...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.57,0:15:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if she appears suddenly before me and says she's a god...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.84,0:15:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, living with a girl under one roof is a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.89,0:16:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I thinking? I can't possibly be with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.23,0:16:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.58,0:16:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm safe as long as I stay with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.54,0:16:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.14,0:16:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, you can stay in this house for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I live alone anyway, but I'll need to give an explanation when my father comes home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.12,0:16:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.31,0:16:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're living together, there are many things that we need to decide upon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.53,0:16:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, the meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.93,0:16:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I eat anything, whether it's seafood or mountain vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.44,0:16:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not talking about your food preference.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.16,0:16:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about who should make the meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.86,0:16:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped; I'll prepare the meals for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, please throw out the rubbish in exchange.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.20,0:16:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Separate the flammable, inflammable, recyclable trash, and the PET bottles...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.46,0:17:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.18,0:17:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't quite understand, but are you making a fool out of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.41,0:17:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was I tricked?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.54,0:17:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And also, the laundry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.43,0:17:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, before you sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take a bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.94,0:17:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bath feels great! I feel like I've come back to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.96,0:18:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Err!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.14,0:18:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.06,0:18:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about your clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.73,0:18:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I wash yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.68,0:18:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks! {please}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, do you have another set of clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.51,0:18:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I don't have them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.11,0:19:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... These.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.19,0:19:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.67,0:19:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I borrowed this from your drawers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should take a bath too-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.83,0:19:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Change out of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.72,0:19:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Refreshing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.27,0:19:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to take a bath, so keep still and watch TV, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.27,0:19:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't answer the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.45,0:19:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be hard for me to explain the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.69,0:19:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.18,0:19:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it's impossible to live together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.05,0:19:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.77,0:19:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.24,0:20:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.90,0:20:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Jin. What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.90,0:20:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi! What do you mean, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.18,0:20:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were absent from school today, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.16,0:20:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's the deadline for the district exhibition.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.16,0:20:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You caught a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.09,0:20:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.92,0:20:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain it to you next time. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something seems wrong. Are you feeling unwell?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.57,0:20:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.01,0:20:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Face the other way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.01,0:20:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is someone else there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.85,0:20:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm alone! Don't worry about me. Anyway, later!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.26,0:20:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.54,0:20:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to answer the phone, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.76,0:20:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aha, so that's the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.72,0:20:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought this is the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.45,0:20:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's also a phone. Anyway, you can't use this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.77,0:20:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin. You'll catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.62,0:20:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please sleep here. I'll sleep in the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.43,0:20:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.90,0:20:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This room has a lock, so it's safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.94,0:21:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, don't touch the things in this room, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.78,0:21:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.32,0:21:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.49,0:21:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.34,0:21:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night, Jin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.21,0:21:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.90,0:21:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.55,0:22:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So even gods...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.85,0:22:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...use the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.29,0:23:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch the next episode of Kannagi too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.56,0:23:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
